										Heimursaga (HEY-mer-saga) is a text-focused, map-centric journaling and fundraising platform designed specifically for travelers. The name "Heimursaga" is derived from the Old Norse 
										words "heimr" meaning "world", and "saga" meaning "story". 
										Heimursaga explorers can write and share journal entries tagged to precise geographic coordinates, and readers or followers can sponsor their favorite explorers via one-time payments 
										or recurring subscriptions. Additional features include waypoint creation, journey mode (grouped entries by route), and private messaging (in development).

