											But the map is soulless without the <i>stories</i>, those remarkable things that happened <i>here</i>. <br><br>The explorer knows the value of a story too, and he wants nothing more than to add his own to the map. It is the stories that inspire the ones back home. 
											It is the stories that generate the means and will to push the edges of the map ever further into the unknown. <br><br><b>This platform is 
											dedicated to the map, to the stories, and most of all, to the explorers.</b></i>

